1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,640
Lluvia,

2
00:00:00,640 --> 00:00:00,960
bici,

3
00:00:00,960 --> 00:00:02,080
Valencia...

4
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:02,560
y algo que

5
00:00:02,560 --> 00:00:03,240
no debería estar

6
00:00:03,240 --> 00:00:04,040
ahí fuera.

7
00:00:04,040 --> 00:00:04,720
Me pilla el agua

8
00:00:04,720 --> 00:00:05,640
pedaleando.

9
00:00:05,640 --> 00:00:06,520
Pero sigo.

10
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:06,720
Y entre

11
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:07,840
la lluvia...

12
00:00:07,840 --> 00:00:08,840
una nevera.

13
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:09,320
Grande.

14
00:00:09,320 --> 00:00:10,680
Aparentemente entera.

15
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:11,520
Pero cuando

16
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:12,440
me acerco...

17
00:00:12,440 --> 00:00:13,480
le habían arrancado

18
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:13,880
el motor.

19
00:00:13,880 --> 00:00:14,480
Alguien la sacó

20
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:15,400
a la calle.

21
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:16,080
Y la persona

22
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:16,680
que la habría

23
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:18,280
recogido completa...

24
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,240
nunca se enteró

25
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:20,240
de que existía.

26
00:00:20,240 --> 00:00:20,880
Mientras,

27
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:21,760
otro pasó

28
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,160
y le sacó

29
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:22,760
lo único

30
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:23,600
que podía vender

31
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,800
como chatarra.

32
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,280
Lo que queda

33
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,040
ya no vale nada.

34
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:26,680
Pero hace

35
00:00:26,680 --> 00:00:27,400
unos días,

36
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:27,960
esa nevera

37
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:28,760
enfriaba.

38
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,240
Y hay gente

39
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:29,760
a pocas calles

40
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:30,600
que la habría querido

41
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,360
tal cual.

42
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:32,080
Solo faltaba

43
00:00:32,080 --> 00:00:32,360
el puente

44
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:33,240
entre los dos.

45
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:33,760
¿Sabéis cómo

46
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:35,040
se evita esto?

47
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:35,520
En Givore,

48
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:36,160
compartes lo que

49
00:00:36,160 --> 00:00:37,240
ya no necesitas.

50
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:37,640
Lo subes

51
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:38,560
en un momento...

52
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:39,760
y quien esté cerca,

53
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:40,760
lo encuentra.

54
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:41,840
Así de directo.

55
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:42,840
Esa nevera

56
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:43,360
habría llegado

57
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:43,960
entera

58
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:44,880
a otra cocina.

59
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,560
En vez de eso...

60
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:46,560
chatarra

61
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:47,240
bajo la lluvia.

62
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,480
Tenerla instalada

63
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:49,200
merece la pena.

64
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,280
Para cuando tengáis

65
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:50,640
algo que

66
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,600
ya no uséis.

67
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,160
Givore.

